  "keyFeatures": [
    "Full Structure-from-Motion pipeline: feature extraction, matching, and incremental reconstruction",
    "Dense reconstruction via multi-view stereo and stereo fusion",
    "RANSAC-based geometric estimators: absolute pose, essential/fundamental/homography matrix, two-view geometry",
    "Scene object API mirroring COLMAP C++: Reconstruction, Camera, Image, Point3D, Database",
    "SIFT feature extraction with optional GPU acceleration (CUDA)",
    "Configurable options via Python dicts or typed option objects",
    "Supports Linux, macOS (Intel & Apple Silicon), and Windows via PyPI wheels"
  ],
